{
  "stem": "19895.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 93.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I understood the mechanics of a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And out of several bicycles, I put together a bicycle which was functioning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was going for a mile or so before this event happened with the Russians tanks and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I also encountered on-- on the trip with the people who were Russians on that truck who were taking me to whatever location they were going, a-- a surrounded area where Russians were having behind some makeshift fences, all kind of people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the truck stopped there, and I was walking around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from inside, some people shouted at me, get away, because they round you up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Russians are producing here a certain number of people whom they need to transport back to Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they round up anybody and everybody for God knows what reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So you-- you just get away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I just went back to my little Russian truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I was pre-warned what happens.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was indeed truth, because many years later, many years later, I was a physician by then, worked in Budapest in a hospital, where a doctor who joined our staff was somebody who was member of the-- well, he was on the Russian front with the forced labor units.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then he was in a concentration camp somewhere on the Austrian border.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when he was freed by the Russians, he was rounded up by some other Russians, taken to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it took him two years to be freed and returned to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, that was Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Krausz, Joszef, Joseph Krausz, who told us that story.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when he came home, he was looking for his wife, whom he found.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
